155
00:07:01,566 --> 00:07:04,033
and then execute this line of code.

156
00:07:04,033 --> 00:07:05,166
After execution,

157
00:07:05,166 --> 00:07:07,100
we can type "pipeline" at the bottom

158
00:07:07,100 --> 00:07:09,766
to call the AI ​​model we want to use. The

159
00:07:09,766 --> 00:07:12,933
first parameter is the "Task" type, which is the

160
00:07:12,933 --> 00:07:16,466
