170
00:07:41,433 --> 00:07:43,366
Finally, we use the `print` syntax

171
00:07:43,366 --> 00:07:45,966
to display the analysis results on the screen.

172
00:07:45,966 --> 00:07:47,900
Okay, let's do a test. The

173
00:07:47,900 --> 00:07:49,300
first time we run it, it will take a while

