175
00:07:54,366 --> 00:07:55,233
After it finishes running,

176
00:07:55,233 --> 00:07:57,766
we can see the analysis results below, showing that the

177
00:07:57,766 --> 00:07:59,933
AI ​​has 99% confidence that

178
00:07:59,933 --> 00:08:02,966
the text expresses a "positive" sentiment.

179
00:08:02,966 --> 00:08:04,900
However, you might find this analysis result

