181
00:08:07,700 --> 00:08:09,900
So, we can consider adjusting the code

182
00:08:09,900 --> 00:08:12,433
to extract the keyword "positive"

183
00:08:12,433 --> 00:08:14,233
and change it to Chinese.

184
00:08:14,233 --> 00:08:17,666
So, I entered a set of square brackets and 0 after the original syntax to

185
00:08:17,666 --> 00:08:20,700
indicate that we want to extract the first set of data within the square brackets. The

186
00:08:20,700 --> 00:08:23,166
data's label name is "label."

187
00:08:23,166 --> 00:08:25,066
Then I pressed Ctrl + Enter to

188
00:08:25,066 --> 00:08:27,033
