for example, complaining that no one is commenting on my posts, the

199
00:08:54,333 --> 00:08:58,366
AI ​​will interpret it as expressing "negative emotions."

200
00:08:58,366 --> 00:09:01,433
Google Colab, while very convenient, is primarily designed for

201
00:09:01,433 --> 00:09:04,433
