222
00:09:54,600 --> 00:09:56,900
After downloading and installing VS Code,

223
00:09:56,900 --> 00:09:59,100
you can open it directly.

224
00:10:01,200 --> 00:10:03,200
First, create a new folder on your desktop or anywhere else

225
00:10:03,200 --> 00:10:05,200
