230
00:10:15,033 --> 00:10:17,466
Since running AI models locally

231
00:10:17,466 --> 00:10:20,366
requires installing some special packages and tools,

232
00:10:20,366 --> 00:10:23,666
to prevent these tools from affecting other projects on your computer,

233
00:10:23,666 --> 00:10:26,833
