235
00:10:29,266 --> 00:10:32,166
So, I go to the sidebar, open the extensions panel,

236
00:10:32,166 --> 00:10:35,866
enter "Python" as the keyword to install its extensions,

237
00:10:35,866 --> 00:10:38,733
and then press Ctrl + Shift + P

238
00:10:38,733 --> 00:10:41,166
to select "Create Virtual Environment." For

239
00:10:41,166 --> 00:10:42,766
